<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 04:09:17 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>对于以色列人来说不幸的是，内塔尼亚胡只有在有好消息时才会出现</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/unfortunately-for-israelis-netanyahu-only-shows-up-when-theres-good-news/0000018f-f96c-d084-abef-ff6d2db20000</link><description>当以色列军队大胆营救人质时，内塔尼亚胡出现在每张照片中，并在每台电视上发表讲话。但正如一名死去人质的父亲雄辩而悲惨地说的那样，“当结局不好时，首相就不会出现。”他也不打电话”</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 02:59:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/unfortunately-for-israelis-netanyahu-only-shows-up-when-theres-good-news/0000018f-f96c-d084-abef-ff6d2db20000</guid></item><item><title>警方在特拉维夫呼吁人质交易的抗议活动中使用高压水枪进行逮捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article-live/police-use-water-cannons-make-arrests-at-tel-aviv-protest-calling-for-hostage-deal/0000018f-fab3-d3fb-a1af-ffbb4ead0000</link><description>从加沙获救的四名人质被送往以色列医院，情况良好 ■ 以色列特种部队军官在救援行动中身亡 ■ 战时内阁部长甘茨推迟宣布离开政府 ■ 哈马斯报告加沙中部有 200 多人死亡 ■ 以色列各地发生示威活动反对政府，支持人质协议 ■ 美国否认在以色列国防军加沙人质营救行动中使用人道主义码头</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 02:22:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article-live/police-use-water-cannons-make-arrests-at-tel-aviv-protest-calling-for-hostage-deal/0000018f-fab3-d3fb-a1af-ffbb4ead0000</guid></item><item><title>对于厌倦战争的以色列人来说，从加沙解救四名人质是一剂强心剂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/rescue-of-four-hostages-from-gaza-a-greatly-needed-shot-in-the-arm-for-war-weary-israelis/0000018f-f97b-df2e-a5df-ff7f10670000</link><description>虽然这一成就肯定会鼓舞仍在加沙作战的以色列国防军士兵的斗志，但这并不预示着战争方式的战略改变 — — 并可能导致哈马斯在停火谈判中加强其要求</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 21:57:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/rescue-of-four-hostages-from-gaza-a-greatly-needed-shot-in-the-arm-for-war-weary-israelis/0000018f-f97b-df2e-a5df-ff7f10670000</guid></item><item><title>美国向以色列提供营救人质情报，但参与程度尚不清楚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/u-s-provided-intelligence-to-israel-for-hostage-rescue-but-involvement-is-unclear/0000018f-f943-de5e-a5ef-fdc7ef1b0000</link><description>以色列和美国官员指出，美国参与了以色列在加沙的人质营救任务的情报收集，但声称显示援助卡车和作为行动一部分的美国建造的码头的图像招致了批评，因为人质交易的未来已成定局。在空中</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 21:08:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/u-s-provided-intelligence-to-israel-for-hostage-rescue-but-involvement-is-unclear/0000018f-f943-de5e-a5ef-fdc7ef1b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列官员不确定救援行动将如何影响与哈马斯的谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/unclear-whether-rescue-will-aid-or-delay-deal-to-free-remaining-hostages/0000018f-f94b-dc3c-a9cf-f97fec3b0000</link><description>以色列和调解员正在等待哈马斯对乔·拜登提出的“以色列计划”的正式回应，消息人士称哈马斯的“同意”将对本杰明·内塔尼亚胡施加巨大压力</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 20:07:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/unclear-whether-rescue-will-aid-or-delay-deal-to-free-remaining-hostages/0000018f-f94b-dc3c-a9cf-f97fec3b0000</guid></item><item><title>获救的以色列人质诺亚·阿加玛尼与身患绝症的母亲团聚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/rescued-israeli-hostage-noa-argamani-reunited-with-her-terminally-ill-mother/0000018f-f909-df2e-a5df-ff7d532c0000</link><description>哈马斯上周发布的一段视频中可以听到诺亚·阿加马尼 (Noa Argamani) 的声音，八个月后，周六，他与另外三名人质在以色列的一次行动中从加沙获救。</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 19:08:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/rescued-israeli-hostage-noa-argamani-reunited-with-her-terminally-ill-mother/0000018f-f909-df2e-a5df-ff7d532c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列各地数万人抗议，呼吁达成人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/tens-of-thousands-protest-across-israel-call-for-govt-to-accept-hostage-deal/0000018f-f90b-dc3c-a9cf-f93f2bcf0000</link><description>周六晚上，以色列各地爆发了抗议活动，在场人士呼吁达成协议，归还剩余 120 名人质并提前举行选举。警方在海法驱散反战抗议者，并在特拉维夫逮捕了33名反战抗议者</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 18:56:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/tens-of-thousands-protest-across-israel-call-for-govt-to-accept-hostage-deal/0000018f-f90b-dc3c-a9cf-f93f2bcf0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列大胆救援行动证明：人质还活着，只有达成协议才能拯救他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-rescue-operation-proves-hostages-are-still-alive-only-a-deal-will-save-them/0000018f-f8de-d084-abef-fedfc8280000</link><description>本杰明·内塔尼亚胡周六赶到示巴医院与被释放的人质合影，但他尚未会见上周宣布死亡的人质的家人。与此同时，总理的喉舌已经在利用救援行动来抹黑领导人的竞争对手</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 18:34:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-rescue-operation-proves-hostages-are-still-alive-only-a-deal-will-save-them/0000018f-f8de-d084-abef-fedfc8280000</guid></item><item><title>由于加沙战争和内塔尼亚胡的政策，以色列妇女权利降至新低</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/womens-rights-in-israel-at-a-new-low-due-to-gaza-war-and-netanyahus-policies/0000018f-ed6f-dd70-a7df-fd6f1f8c0000</link><description>以色列民主研究所的一份报告称，由于 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击、随后发生的加沙战争以及国内家庭暴力，以色列的暴力侵害妇女行为将在 2024 年出现前所未有的激增，该报告还警告称，以色列将妇女排除在外。决策论坛中的女性</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 18:00:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/womens-rights-in-israel-at-a-new-low-due-to-gaza-war-and-netanyahus-policies/0000018f-ed6f-dd70-a7df-fd6f1f8c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队称光天化日之下同时从加沙公寓救出人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-hostages-rescued-from-gaza-apartments-simultaneously-in-broad-daylight/0000018f-f8aa-d084-abef-feeb55250000</link><description>以色列军队表示，根据情报，这次任务的准备工作在几周前就开始了，他们按照恩德培行动等模式进行了训练。以色列军队遭到包括火箭弹在内的猛烈射击，一名军官受重伤，后来因伤重不治身亡</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 17:54:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-hostages-rescued-from-gaza-apartments-simultaneously-in-broad-daylight/0000018f-f8aa-d084-abef-feeb55250000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 246 天：以色列在加沙中部的行动中救出四名人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-246-four-hostages-rescued-in-israeli-operation-in-central-gaza/0000018f-f8b9-d7d0-af9f-fdfd6b950000</link><description>以色列在加沙中部的行动中四名人质被生还；一名特种部队军官被杀 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部：210 名巴勒斯坦人在以色列国防军行动中丧生，400 多人受伤 ■ 以色列医院官员：获救人质状况良好且“精神状态良好” ■ 以下是 245 天后您需要了解的信息战争</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 16:58:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-246-four-hostages-rescued-in-israeli-operation-in-central-gaza/0000018f-f8b9-d7d0-af9f-fdfd6b950000</guid></item><item><title>以色列特种部队军官在加沙解救人质行动中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-special-forces-officer-killed-in-gaza-operation-to-free-hostages/0000018f-f86d-d93d-abbf-fa7f77d30000</link><description>10月7日，总督察阿农·兹莫拉在以色列南部奋力击退恐怖分子，在成功解救四名人质后身亡</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 15:54:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-special-forces-officer-killed-in-gaza-operation-to-free-hostages/0000018f-f86d-d93d-abbf-fa7f77d30000</guid></item><item><title>八个月零一天后：四名人质与亲人团聚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/after-eight-months-and-one-day-four-israeli-hostages-reunited-with-their-loved-ones/0000018f-f859-d93d-abbf-fa7b39e70000</link><description>诺亚·阿加马尼 (Noa Argamani)、阿尔莫格·梅厄·扬 (Almog Meir Jan)、安德烈·科兹洛夫 (Andrey Kozlov) 和什洛米·齐夫 (Shlomi Ziv) 在示巴医疗中心与亲人团聚</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 15:34:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/after-eight-months-and-one-day-four-israeli-hostages-reunited-with-their-loved-ones/0000018f-f859-d93d-abbf-fa7b39e70000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯称以色列在加沙中部解救人质行动中至少有210人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/hamas-says-at-least-210-killed-in-israeli-hostage-rescue-operation-in-central-gaza/0000018f-f84c-d084-abef-fe4d4a760000</link><description>在解救四名以色列人质的行动中，以色列国防军从空中、海上和陆地袭击了努塞拉特和代尔巴拉赫。哈马斯卫生部称，死亡人数预计还会上升，附近医院难以应对不断增加的伤亡人数</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 15:26:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/hamas-says-at-least-210-killed-in-israeli-hostage-rescue-operation-in-central-gaza/0000018f-f84c-d084-abef-fe4d4a760000</guid></item><item><title>以色列甘茨取消预期宣布退出内塔尼亚胡政府的新闻发布会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/gantz-cancels-expected-press-conference-announcing-departure-from-netanyahu-government/0000018f-f828-df2e-a5df-fe7dbe180000</link><description>在成功营救四名以色列人质后，甘茨推迟了宣布这一消息的时间，但预计将在未来几天内选择新的日期</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 14:21:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/gantz-cancels-expected-press-conference-announcing-departure-from-netanyahu-government/0000018f-f828-df2e-a5df-fe7dbe180000</guid></item><item><title>自10月7日以来，以色列特种部队解救了哈马斯在加沙扣押的四名人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-forces-rescue-four-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas/0000018f-f78b-d660-af9f-ffbfb2190000</link><description>获救人质诺亚·阿加马尼 (Noa Argamani)、阿尔莫格·梅厄·扬 (Almog Meir Jan)、安德烈·科兹洛夫 (Andrey Kozlov) 和什洛米·齐夫 (Shlomi Ziv) 于 10 月 7 日在 Nova 音乐节上被绑架，并在以色列的一次行动中获救，行动之前进行了数周的情报收集</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 11:33:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-forces-rescue-four-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas/0000018f-f78b-d660-af9f-ffbfb2190000</guid></item><item><title>定居者将这个巴勒斯坦家庭驱逐出村庄。然后恐怖又开始了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-06-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/settlers-expelled-them-from-their-village-then-the-terror-began-all-over-again-again/0000018f-f67e-d84e-adbf-f77f421e0000</link><description>由于害怕定居者，一个巴勒斯坦牧羊家庭在战争开始后逃离了南希伯伦山的村庄。他们带着羊群搬迁，但在新的避难所却找不到任何缓解。上周，一名年轻男子遭到武装蒙面定居者袭击后入院治疗</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 06:51:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-06-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/settlers-expelled-them-from-their-village-then-the-terror-began-all-over-again-again/0000018f-f67e-d84e-adbf-f77f421e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国库已成为极端正统学校系统的ATM机，助长腐败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.highlight/israels-treasury-has-become-the-haredi-school-systems-atm-encouraging-corruption/0000018f-f50f-df2e-a5df-f77ff10c0000</link><description>如果它承担了极端正统教育网络所欠下的大部分债务，财政部将向其发出信号，疏忽是没有代价的</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 06:13:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.highlight/israels-treasury-has-become-the-haredi-school-systems-atm-encouraging-corruption/0000018f-f50f-df2e-a5df-f77ff10c0000</guid></item><item><title>警方在特拉维夫呼吁人质交易的抗议活动中使用高压水枪进行逮捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article-live/idf-drone-fired-from-lebanon-fell-in-open-area-in-north-after-failed-interception-attempt/0000018f-f5d1-d190-af8f-fff30f860000</link><description>从加沙获救的四名人质被送往以色列医院，情况良好 ■ 以色列特种部队军官在救援行动中身亡 ■ 战时内阁部长甘茨推迟宣布离开政府 ■ 哈马斯报告加沙中部有 200 多人死亡 ■ 以色列各地发生示威活动反对政府，支持人质协议 ■ 美国否认在以色列国防军加沙人质营救行动中使用人道主义码头</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 03:35:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article-live/idf-drone-fired-from-lebanon-fell-in-open-area-in-north-after-failed-interception-attempt/0000018f-f5d1-d190-af8f-fff30f860000</guid></item><item><title>“你支持恐怖主义”：10 月 7 日事件后，犹太学校的以色列阿拉伯教师面临迫害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-arab-teachers-in-jewish-schools-face-persecution-in-wake-of-oct-7/0000018f-f4d7-d84e-adbf-f5df0fe90000</link><description>尽管与以色列社会有疏离感，并且在某些情况下，个人安全感下降，但犹太教育系统中的阿拉伯教师仍然相信自己有使命要完成</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 23:33:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-arab-teachers-in-jewish-schools-face-persecution-in-wake-of-oct-7/0000018f-f4d7-d84e-adbf-f5df0fe90000</guid></item></channel></rss>